{"tid":839761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大學體育館「打野戰」情侶乾柴烈火纏綿片段瘋傳","createTime":"2018-09-28T07:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T06:05:58.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"92c16b3dd88469057c7cb94844ef04a0036a839b","tid":839761,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:31:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NqVq0AaSkE04zGq3v5QVmA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2018-09/dbcc9300-c2d5-11e8-b351-1e0da3a008a2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNqVq0AaSkE04zGq3v5QVmA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2018-09%2Fdbcc9300-c2d5-11e8-b351-1e0da3a008a2&h=b5f32f3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】內地網絡中秋節前一天（23日）瘋傳一段短片，北京郵電大學兩名學生在體育館直接脫光「打野戰」，被躲在牆角暗中觀察的人拍了2分8秒的短片，短片上拍攝的玻璃門，上面清晰的看到「北郵體育館」的字樣。片段曝光後，立即引來網民熱烈討論，有網民冷嘲：「窮到開不起房嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n據新浪微博上流出北郵體育館2分8秒的短片中，兩位北郵學生在體育館直接脫光乾柴烈火，兩人纏綿中竟然不知道被誰拍攝了下來，然後被人發到了網絡上了，於是北郵體育館的短片瘋傳了。該對男女在走廊附近，旁邊就是室外，體育館門口的露天廣場，但他們旁若無人在此「打野戰」。事發現場的體育館其實有不少人的，中秋放假，但大部分學生也沒有回家，還是會在學校的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E9%A4%A8-%E6%89%93%E9%87%8E%E6%88%B0-%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E4%B9%BE%E6%9F%B4%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB%E7%BA%8F%E7%B6%BF%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-021900152.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E9%25AB%2594%25E8%2582%25B2%25E9%25A4%25A8-%25E6%2589%2593%25E9%2587%258E%25E6%2588%25B0-%25E6%2583%2585%25E4%25BE%25B6%25E4%25B9%25BE%25E6%259F%25B4%25E7%2583%2588%25E7%2581%25AB%25E7%25BA%258F%25E7%25B6%25BF%25E7%2589%2587%25E6%25AE%25B5%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3-021900152.html&d=B4nGfHi%2BlHStSkvHnZa087%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=dba28393\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%B8%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2%E9%A4%A8-%E6%89%93%E9%87%8E%E6%88%B0-%E6%83%85%E4%BE%B6%E4%B9%BE%E6%9F%B4%E7%83%88%E7%81%AB%E7%BA%8F%E7%B6%BF%E7%89%87%E6%AE%B5%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3-021900152.html</a><br />\n有網民留言指，片中的男主角是北京郵電大學學生；女主角則是距離該校不遠的北京航空航天大學學生。當時正值中秋節假期，很少學生要上課，但偶爾仍有學生出入校園，而該對男女可能以為放假不會有人看見，才會膽敢在公眾地方這樣做，殊不知恰巧有人經過，更舉機拍下過程。"},{"pid":"e3f53df10e9a77020a1684e464a896f5047847b2","tid":839761,"uid":48,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾耐"},{"pid":"6e6f86fa8f5d8b019c855784a5ea4a11dc407af3","tid":839761,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"e3f53df10e9a77020a1684e464a896f5047847b2","tid":839761,"uid":48,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"有你咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e340a82960095114859389fb16b50bf0e96d721b","tid":839761,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6e6f86fa8f5d8b019c855784a5ea4a11dc407af3","tid":839761,"uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"e3f53df10e9a77020a1684e464a896f5047847b2","tid":839761,"uid":48,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"樓主坐左幾耐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:33:54.000Z","msg":"有你咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T07:38:57.000Z","msg":"單嘢都起碼五日前，真係啱啱放出嚟？？<br />\n<br />\n劉馬車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6013de20c967cfc11c639bb34f80adb153b8a338","tid":839761,"uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e340a82960095114859389fb16b50bf0e96d721b","tid":839761,"uid":68081,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"6e6f86fa8f5d8b019c855784a5ea4a11dc407af3","tid":839761,"uid":184679